NCC Group plc - Strategy, SWOT and Corporate Finance Report, is a source of comprehensive company data and information. The report covers the company's structure, operation, SWOT analysis, product and service offerings and corporate actions, providing a 360deg view of the company.Key FindingsDetailed information on NCC Group plc required for business and competitor intelligence needsA study of the major internal and external factors affecting NCC Group plc in the form of a SWOT analysisAn in-depth view of the business model of NCC Group plc including a breakdown and examination of key business segmentsIntelligence on NCC Group plc's mergers and acquisitions (MandA), strategic partnerships and alliances, capital raising, private equity transactions, and financial and legal advisorsNews about NCC Group plc, such as business expansion, restructuring, and contract winsLarge number of easy-to-grasp charts and graphs that present important data and key trendsReasons to Get this ReportGain understanding of NCC Group plc and the factors that influence its strategies.Track strategic initiatives of the company and latest corporate news and actions.Assess NCC Group plc as a prospective partner, vendor or supplier.Support sales activities by understanding your customers' businesses better.Stay up to date on NCC Group plc's business structure, strategy and prospects.Report HighlightsNCC Group plc (NCC or "the group") is a global information assurance services provider engaged in offering escrow, verification, security consulting, website performance, software testing and domain services. The group primarily operates in the UK, Europe as well as in North America and Australia. It is headquartered in Manchester, the UK and employed approximately 1,388 people as of FY2015.
